[11] Cholera - Mali
Date: Sat 6 Aug 2011
Source: Bloomberg News [edited]
http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-06/mali-cholera-death-toll-rises-to-23-health-directorate-says.html


Mali's death toll from a cholera epidemic has reached 23, with 419
cases recorded so far, the National Directorate of Health announced
today [6 Aug 2011] on public radio.

